     <section aria-labelledby="intro-header" class="col-xs-12 main-section" role="region">
      <header class="main-section-header" id="intro-header">
       <h2 class="top">
        The Center for Energy Research creates solutions to the growing challenges of energy supply and utilization in our society.
       </h2>
      </header>
     </section>
     <section aria-labelledby="main-region" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 main-section pull-left" role="region">
      <article class="main-section-content" id="main-region">
       <h2>
        Welcome,
       </h2>
       <div style="margin-left: 15px; margin-right: 15px;">
        <p>
         Our Vision is to build an internationally recognized center of excellence by fostering interdisciplinary research, developing visibility for UCSD as a leading institution in energy studies, and creating educational programs in energy technologies.
        </p>
        <p>
         We welcome your participation in our Center as a student, researcher, outreach partner, or in another capacity. Please browse our site and contact us if you don’t find what you need.
        </p>
        <em>
         - Farhat Beg,
        </em>
        <em>
         CER Director
        </em>
        <h2>
        </h2>
       </div>
       <div class="contact-block" style="background: #f7f9f9; margin: 15px; border: 1.5px solid #e2e9e9;">
